This repo is part of Paulo's Agent Hub.

Before editing:
- Read `AGENTS.md`.
- Read `CODEX_RULES.md` if present.
- Read `.brain/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` if present.
- Read `.brain/HUB_COUNCIL_CONTEXT.md` if present.
- Read `.brain/CURSOR_BACKGROUND_AGENT_CONTEXT.md` if present.
- Treat Linear as the live source for issue/project/cycle/status when a connector or issue link is available.

Project identity:
- Registry id: `pierrondi-site`
- Linear hint: `pierrondi.dev Public Site (AGE-1486)`
- Obsidian note: `02_Projects/pierrondi-site`

Guardrails:
- Preserve existing user and agent changes.
- Do not touch secrets, `.env` values, credentials, production deploys, App Store submission, TestFlight upload, paid campaigns, social publishing, migrations or destructive git operations.
- Keep work scoped to one issue or one small task.
- Stop and report if more than 5 files need changes.
- Update or add tests when production code changes.

Final output must include:
- What changed.
- Files touched.
- Commands/tests run.
- Risks or blockers.
- Suggested Obsidian/Linear update.
